info.name: Text Generation
info.description: The Gemini API can generate text output when provided text, images, video, and audio as input. This guide shows you how to generate text using the [generateContent](https://ai.google.dev/api/rest/v1/models/generateContent) and [streamGenerateContent](https://ai.google.dev/api/rest/v1/models/streamGenerateContent) methods.
